# CI / governance notes:
# - Any module claiming to implement or modify the EcoNet reward pipeline
#   must reference this design_artifact_id and pass guards for:
#   - zero_personal_gain
#   - public_good_sinks_only
#   - roh_ceiling_enforced
#   - neurorights_compliant
# - Prometheus-Praxis and Perkunos-Nexus jointly veto any change that
#   weakens these constraints.
